Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:55.97,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}The kindness that he once saw is now gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:23:06.90,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}He steps forward alone, looking only at his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:22.29,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\3c&HCB6D14&\bord2\blur2}He always listened to the song that disappeared by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:37.52,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}He chased forever those footprints we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That child said, "I want to see the ocean."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to do many things for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but I couldn't do a single thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,even though summer had just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san, it's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad that Kirishima-san recovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, when I saw that feather, I also had a kinda mysterious feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been out of it ever since you woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw a dream of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:02:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, do you still have those dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The dream last night was different from anything from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The moon was floating, and it was really bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to climb the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My entire body was throbbing and trying to ascend higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, I heard voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Voices?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The voices of many people were trying to restrain me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They echoed in my ears, so I couldn't climb anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, be carefu-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great, isn't it, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how it's walking without any strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It tripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It stood! It stood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how kids should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, shouldn't you be by Kano's side?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko piko piko piko pikori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's going to school to take care of the animals today...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why are we having a normal conversation like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Doll-san, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Handshake, handshake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what a harmonious relationship is like, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked for free again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That Misuzu is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:06.28,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to say something, do it after you swallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Misuzu come this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamio-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you make hamburgers tomorrow too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What a gluttonous person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You let go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you able to use the shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get the keys to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was the stationmaster here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's not working here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he find a different job?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,as a token of apology for what just happened, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:33.24,Note,,0,0,0,,[On the envelope: Rice Ticket]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the bottle I found yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is stardust,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,sand shaped like baby stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, is it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It rustles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki-san too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can have one too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, the three of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This sand is something that my father gave me when I was still small.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then isn't it something precious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if it's you and Michiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that Kamio-san has already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I... see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that she stayed at school this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. Kunisaki-san, are you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome... to the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars are out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the other club members?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the only club member.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The only?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm Club President.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a really selective club.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is the first time that I've brought her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going out of your way to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted the three of us to get together and observe the stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because it seems that she likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She talks about you constantly when she is with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She likes you, Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how she feels,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because she is half of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Half of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru and I have always spent our time together like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki-san, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...always travelling alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever spent time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The happiness of being with someone other than yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The joy of being able to live for someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even someone like me should have,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,though it was in the distant past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmhmm, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's Michiru Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to escort me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you dislike tall girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Since having a nice body is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I happen to think of it a little boastfully too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Happen to think about it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Happen to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The taller you are, the closer you are to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for escorting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful walking home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that person is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A new member of the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I carried groceries for her the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for having you go to the trouble of walking my daughter home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come inside, Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner is already prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tohno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.57,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:32.37,Note,,0,0,0,,[Sign: I'm working hard on my homework.]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yukito-san, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's night right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have told me that supplemental classes were going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're keeping a picture diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my choice of assignment for the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you betray me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Weak soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow you to shamelessly act against this progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Members of the troop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If I die, who will do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really want it, kill me and take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Geh! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the best part!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to play cards with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:13:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: Yukito says "No matter what" in the Kansai dialect often used in stand up comedies (and by Haruko).]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what do you want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Poker?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it something simple that doesn't require thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's play Concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can play.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to try my hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to try my hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you step outside for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been like this ever since she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She becomes like that when she's on the verge of being friends with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When she's on the verge of being friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had the doctor at the clinic look at her, and I've even tried going to a big hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:15:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told it was probably a psychological thing and that she'd get better when she got older,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but she actually had an attack at school today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was contacted at my workplace, so I went to pick her up on my bike and took her straight home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was expecting and hoping that she'd be all right with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,since she's all right when she's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll have these attacks as long as I'm here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try distancing myself for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her that I'll continue walking her to and from school just like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come eat every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't able to stay at my house because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you lonely being by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm alone when I sleep and when I get up, but I'm all right because the number of my friends increased without my knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You have some friends too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because I start crying when I'm about to make a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone always runs away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have Haruko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She... isn't my real mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruko-san is actually my aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was dumped onto her because I was a weird kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruko-san didn't want me, but I ended up living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I don't want to cause her trouble, we live separately under one roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really a bother, so I'm always playing by myself to avoid causing any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for weird juices, or playing cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi isn't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She has school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll come eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not supposed to be at school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:17:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:00.55,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Indirect kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk about adult stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Bubbles are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're empty, just like the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try going to Tohno's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi's... house?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If she isn't coming, we should go see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go to her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I have to pick Misuzu up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for walking me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have to excuse myself here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not eating dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have somewhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I met you yesterday, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a new member of the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm running an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you call your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Has she gone somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We... don't have a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you've got the right house?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joking, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here, skipping your part-time job?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohno-san's mother was troubled in her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I occasionally monitored her condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She convinced herself that her eldest daughter, Minagi-san, is her second daughter who passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quite a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But there seems to have been a sudden change in her condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time that she realised that her younger daughter wasn't living, she forgot about Minagi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside of her, she believed that both of her daughters never existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to have a younger sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a precious younger sister named Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was sad because I was close to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Michiru who was about to be born was supposed to fill the hole in her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had one wish, what would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a younger sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother lost a vent for her feelings, so she chose to continue watching a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And I... was a fragment of that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But last night, she apparently saw herself in a dream having a miscarriage of Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Kirishima-sensei, Mother accepted reality after seeing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning, when she saw me, Mother said,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end of my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the end of my dream in which I lived as Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My wings have now forgotten how to fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,because I always just pretended to flap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:22:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a use for wings that cannot fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're more suited to travels than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.56,0:23:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you come with me, Tohno?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.15,0:23:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good being like this, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.57,0:23:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to show you the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.49,0:24:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the real world, not a dream world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything started from my sin.
